title: When Will Each Rookie QB Make Their First Start?
itunes:title: When Will Each Rookie QB Make Their First Start?
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Gregg Rosenthal, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling & Patrick Claybon - recap the latest news from around the league, including Jameis Winston’s now official suspension (6:25), outgoing Panthers owner Jerry Richardson fined $2.75 million (13:30), Danielle Hunter’s new contract (18:00) and a few trope alerts. Marc reads a letter from a podcast listener (31:00) and the heroes debate which holiday each rookie quarterback will make their first start (35:00).

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
